&lt;li&gt;Write and review code, work in sprints (managing tickets/blockers), and coordinate with the other intern.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively use AI-assisted coding tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demo working products to leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
