&lt;li&gt;Prior LLM/AI API integration experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with event-driven/serverless architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to agent frameworks/multi-step AI workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
